Set price to 100
Set quantity to 2
Set tax rate to 0.1
Set rounded units to the result of round(price * quantity / 3)
Set rounded units precise to the result of round(price * quantity / 3, 2)
Set floored units to the result of floor(price * quantity / 3)
Set ceiled units to the result of ceil(price * quantity / 3)
Set total always is the result of round(price * quantity * (1 + tax rate), 2)
Print "Rounded units is (rounded units)".
Print "Rounded units precise is (rounded units precise)".
Print "Floored units is (floored units)".
Print "Ceiled units is (ceiled units)".
Print "Total is (total)".
